{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"46d9cb913b","title":"《人民日报》要重视理论工作","origin":"","is_range_date":true,"dates":[{"id":"93e9bbf4c6","index":1,"year":1964,"month":12,"day":null,"articleId":"46d9cb913b"},{"id":"bba01dc5a0","index":0,"year":1964,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"46d9cb913b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji46","name":"毛泽东全集第46卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/46-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji46":{"comments":[{"id":"0e3483226a","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"46d9cb913b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"本篇是毛泽东对吴冷西儿次谈话的一部分。"},{"id":"29487f3657","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"46d9cb913b","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指《关于“用革命精神改进设计工作”的讨论》专栏第六期登出的四篇短文章：《带着党的政策下现场》《走出个人主义的小圈子》《放下“施工指导”的架子，虚心向工人学习》《不能把工厂看成静止不变的东西》。“编后”的题目是：《根本问题在哪里？》。"},{"id":"fc42fd23a4","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"46d9cb913b","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指1964年12月5日一版《卖菜礼记》和短评《领导还是被领导？》。"}],"contents":[{"id":"9fe1ac6f3f","type":"title","text":"《人民日报》要重视理论工作”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"46d9cb913b"},{"id":"0e3483226a","type":"paragraph","text":"《人民日报》要注意发表学术性文章，发表历史、哲学和其他的学术文章。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"46d9cb913b"},{"id":"29487f3657","type":"paragraph","text":"抓苦学，要抓活哲学。我写文章，不大引马克思、列宁怎么说。报纸老引我的话，引来引去，我就不舒服。应该学会用自己的话来写文章。列宁就很少引人家的话，而用自己的话写文章。当然不是说不要引人家的话，是说不要处处都引","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"46d9cb913b"},{"id":"fc42fd23a4","type":"paragraph","text":"（一月八日）","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"46d9cb913b"},{"id":"528ab5c443","type":"paragraph","text":"《人民日报》要搞理论工作，不能只搞政治。《人民日报》最近组织一些学术讨论，这样做好。《人民日报》对教学改革问题发表过文章没有？《文汇报》上一篇文章《不可能什么都懂》，可以看看，可以转载。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"46d9cb913b"},{"id":"816536886e","type":"paragraph","text":"（三月二十二日）","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"46d9cb913b"},{"id":"46fa6c8144","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"46d9cb913b"},{"id":"8c2607ce81","type":"paragraph","text":"现在，《人民日报》有看头了，理论上加强了，也有一些有意思的东西。今天（二十日）二版关于设计讨论的四篇小文章全看了，编者按也写得好。大白菜也上了头条以，很好，要继续努力。《解放军报》《中国青年报》有些短的、生动活泼的、思想性强的文章，要学习。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"46d9cb913b"},{"id":"915a70741a","type":"paragraph","text":"（十二月二十日）","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"46d9cb913b"}],"page":{"id":"8fea71c595","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"46d9cb913b","start":252,"end":253}}}},"__N_SSG":true}